          "settings": {
            "name": "Jessica Mayers",
            "job_title": "Tennis medalist",
            "text": "\u201cButtery smooth leggings, amazing fit, although great for yoga, might not be as suited for more intense workouts as i dont feel tight support around some muscles.\u201d"
