          "settings": {
            "name": "Emily Turner",
            "job_title": "Loyal Customer",
            "text": "Andar's athleisure wear is more than just clothing; it's a confidence boost. Whether I'm hitting the gym or running errands, I feel empowered and stylish. Andar truly elevates my active lifestyle."
