            "job_title": "Loyal Customer",
            "text": "Andar's athleisure collection is a game-changer for me. The perfect blend of comfort and fashion makes every workout a breeze, and I love how effortlessly stylish I feel, even on my busiest days. Andar understands what active women need."
          }
        }
